00:15:22.430 --> 00:15:23.760
e desestabilizando o equilíbrio de Xichuan.

00:15:24.710 --> 00:15:26.790
Lorde Wen, por favor, considere o panorama geral.

00:15:27.070 --> 00:15:27.790
